subject: Fixed Website
msgSnippet: Hi, I managed to get a new server for my Quikscript site, and all links should be working within the next five minutes. I hear cjb.net still creates pop-ups
messageBody:
Hi,

I managed to get a new server for my Quikscript site, and all links
should be working within the next five minutes. I hear cjb.net still
creates pop-ups and banners, I have never noticed them, all I get is
java errors. But then again, I run special banner blocking software
and I work with old browsers.

Anyway, take a look at http://quikscript.teraiten.cjb.net/ (yep,
Quikscript without a c)

/EvQt stym

http://teraiten.cjb.net/
